name: BOHR
description:
BOHR is a decentralized blockchain system that facilitates transactions and development through powerful applications. Solve the bottleneck of the large-scale implementation of the blockchain industry, break technical barriers with fast smart contracts, and open up market interactions with a multi-dimensional ecological structure.
Taking the defi ecology as the starting point, it alleviates the development bottleneck faced by the public chain market and enables a decentralized management ecology.
